Middlesbrough have signed Holland Under-21 winger Yanic Wildschut from Heerenveen.

The 22-year-old has penned a two-year contract at the Riverside Stadium, joining for a fee in the region of £600,000.

Wildschut is a product of Ajax’s academy but never made a senior appearance for the club.

